Social and Teamwork Skills course will give an overview of the social and communication skills in social field, e.g. in the workplace.Objectives/eesmärkid:  Course aims to provide the knowledge about the principles of forming and maintaining relationships, developing collaboration and communicating in challenging situations and conflict situations. In the video-training participants develop skills of active listening and conflict management.Learning outcomes/õpiväljund:  The students develop an understanding of basic interpersonal communication skills, analyse their own communication and cooperation skills during the communication skills training and they  demonstrate improvement in communication skills including listening and responding, managing difference, managing conflict and having ethical communication
